    "Clinical_Features": {
      "text": "New psychiatric symptoms (HSV)\n[2]\nCognitive deficits\nAphasia, amnesia,\nconfusion\nSeizure\nMovement disorder (arboviruses)\nFever\nand meningeal signs are almost always present\nDysuria\nand pyuria (St. Louis encephalitis)\nExtreme\nlethargy\n(West Nile encephalitis)",
