    "Evaluation": {
      "text": "Imaging identifies abnormalities in medial temporal and inferior frontal gray matter in HSV\n[3]\nCT Head\n- edema and petechial hemorrhage\nMRI\n- increased T2 intensity\nLP\nBloody tap consistent with HSV",
      "subsections": {},
      "tables": [],
